As a 30 year veteran of the beer business, Joe is responsible for financial and strategic planning for Andrews Distributing. His career has been painted with 15 successful acquisitions in 15 years and he is excited for future Andrews growth opportunities. Joe holds...



Joe JerniganChief Financial Officer

As a 30 year veteran of the beer business, Joe is responsible for financial and strategic planning for Andrews Distributing. His career has been painted with 15 successful acquisitions in 15 years and he is excited for future Andrews growth opportunities. 
Joe holds a business degree from El Centro College and is a former board member for the Stemmons Corridor Business Assocition. He and his lovely wife have two children and two granddaughters.






Vice President/GM South Texas
