Sean MurphyVice President/GM South Texas

Sean has worked in the beer business for over 25 years and is responsible for the Andrews' South Texas business operations. During his career he has successfully acquired and integrated two distributorships into the Andrews family. Sean also takes pride in mentoring young managers and developing team members. 
Sean holds a Marketing Degree from The University of North Texas and sits on the board for the Corpus Christi Chamber of Commerce. He and his wife Carol have three children.






Vice President of Information Technology
John Ross Read More >>
In overseeing Andrews’ IT department, John is responsible for directing the information and data integrity of the entire Andrews enterprise, which includes all data centers, technical service centers, production and scheduling functions, help desks, communication networks...



John RossVice President of Information Technology

In overseeing Andrews’ IT department, John is responsible for directing the information and data integrity of the entire Andrews enterprise, which includes all data centers, technical service centers, production and scheduling functions, help desks, communication networks, computer program developments and computer systems operations. 
John is a graduate of Texas State University and holds a MBA from Southern Methodist University. He and his wife Courtney have two children.






Vice President of Supply Chain
Dan Betz Read More >>
As Vice President of Supply Chain, Dan oversees the distribution center team, logistics team (focusing on intercompany logistics), and supply chain team. Dan is a leader with more than 25 years of broad, senior-level experience in distribution...



Dan BetzVice President of Supply Chain

As Vice President of Supply Chain, Dan oversees the distribution center team, logistics team (focusing on intercompany logistics), and supply chain team. Dan is a leader with more than 25 years of broad, senior-level experience in distribution, warehouse and supply chain management in various industries including multi-billion dollar Fortune 500 companies in the beverage, automotive, and flooring industries.
Dan graduated with a BBA in Operations Management from Temple University in Philadelphia. He and his wife Suzanne have two daughters.






Vice President of Commericial Strategy
Nick Lake Read More >>
As Vice President of Commercial Strategy, Nick is responsible for supporting the sales, brand and leadership teams with insights, leading indicators and dashboards through the business planning and analytics team.



Nick LakeVice President of Commericial Strategy

As Vice President of Commercial Strategy, Nick is responsible for supporting the sales, brand and leadership teams with insights, leading indicators and dashboards through the business planning and analytics team. This team supports the Andrews brand building mission and the drive to be our customers' most-trusted advisor with shopper and consumer insights to enable decisions that create more value for our retailers.
Nick is a leader with more than 20 years of beer and alcohol industry experience, analyzing industry trends and assisting suppliers, distributors and retail partners with their beer category growth strategies.
Prior to joining Andrews Distributing, Nick was at Procter and Gamble in a variety of sales and sales management positions, Nielsen, where he co-led the beverage alcohol vertical, and Heineken USA, where he led the category development. Nick is a graduate of the University of Minnesota with a Bachelors in Business Administration and an MBA. He and his wife Martha have three children.













